  "3222130": {
    "name": "Who Do Voodoo",
    "steam_appid": 3222130,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222130/extras/7f47cdc0b7be428dac90e318ee53ae8a.webp?t=1771945587\" width=616 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222130/extras/e8beff6e7cc9174ec925d33bd1c57dba.webp?t=1771945587\" width=616 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一款社交推理游戏，在这里制作的卡牌会变成法术。保护盟友、破坏对手，或在魔法生存之战中捉弄所有人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222130/extras/1756a6c2066e5ca1291ac5f88b9aa5b9.poster.avif?t=1771945587\" width=616 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222130/extras/1756a6c2066e5ca1291ac5f88b9aa5b9.webm?t=1771945587\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222130/extras/1756a6c2066e5ca1291ac5f88b9aa5b9.mp4?t=1771945587\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在混乱的多人比赛中与 6 到 16 名玩家一起游戏。每局开始时，你会获得可以在地图中游走时施放的法术卡。有些卡会保护，有些会破坏，还有些只是给所有人制造麻烦。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222130/extras/67a07d704ef3b7ff8a614c0642b09e0e.poster.avif?t=1771945587\" width=616 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222130/extras/67a07d704ef3b7ff8a614c0642b09e0e.webm?t=1771945587\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222130/extras/67a07d704ef3b7ff8a614c0642b09e0e.mp4?t=1771945587\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Who Do Voodoo》具有独特的卡牌制作与动作系统。玩家在地图上自由移动时，会收集魔法材料来制作三种类型的卡牌：善良卡牌用于保护和调查，邪恶卡牌用于破坏和攻击，趣味卡牌用于恶作剧和制造混乱。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222130/extras/7d136a353243258ed408fafb04e23427.poster.avif?t=1771945587\" width=616 height=181 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222130/extras/7d136a353243258ed408fafb04e23427.webm?t=1771945587\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >卡牌会在实时中直接对其他玩家使用，使每一轮都充满动态与不可预测性。社交互动不仅仅是为了欺骗，它也是一种战略工具。玩家必须读懂行为、结成联盟，并在最佳时机采取行动。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222130/extras/d39a8214cba723a7f33a8406aef26d45.poster.avif?t=1771945587\" width=616 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222130/extras/d39a8214cba723a7f33a8406aef26d45.webm?t=1771945587\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222130/extras/d39a8214cba723a7f33a8406aef26d45.mp4?t=1771945587\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你将扮演被困在被诅咒的中世纪城堡里的活体巫毒娃娃，秘密分为两个隐藏的阵营：善良的巫毒和邪恶的巫毒。虚张声势、欺骗、制作魔法卡牌，在这场信任与背叛的高风险较量中智胜对手。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222130/extras/ec82164fa9a3842675ad889eb20b4673.poster.avif?t=1771945587\" width=616 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222130/extras/ec82164fa9a3842675ad889eb20b4673.webm?t=1771945587\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222130/extras/ec82164fa9a3842675ad889eb20b4673.mp4?t=1771945587\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你还可以使用各种皮肤和装饰品自定义你的巫毒娃娃角色，以展现个人风格，并在混乱中脱颖而出。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你会保护无辜者、在暗处散播混乱，还是只是为了好玩而捉弄所有人？在《Who Do Voodoo》中，不要相信任何人，打出你的好牌。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>主要特色：</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>基于团队的隐藏身份：</strong> 玩家会被秘密分为两个对立的阵营：善良巫毒与邪恶巫毒。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>基于卡牌的玩法：</strong> 打出三类卡牌——善良、邪恶和趣味——来保护队友、破坏敌人，或恶作剧所有人。每个行动都至关重要。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>卡牌制作系统：</strong> 在地图上收集物品并将其组合，在比赛中途制作强大或不可预测的卡牌。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>实时玩家互动：</strong> 在实时中对其他玩家使用卡牌。直接且反应迅速的玩法依赖于时机和直觉。通过游戏内语音聊天系统与他人交流，包括临近语音聊天。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>自由探索地图：</strong> 在地图中自由移动，没有固定路径或移动限制。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>WASD 移动与鼠标操作：</strong> 使用 WASD 探索地图，并通过直观的鼠标操作与玩家、卡牌和投票系统互动。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>角色自定义：</strong> 解锁并装备独特的皮肤和装饰品，个性化你的巫毒娃娃，展现你的风格。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>当前一张地图（更多即将推出）：</strong> 游戏目前包含一张详细地图，未来更新将推出更多主题地图。</p></li></ul>",
